<L>__{exterior rez's house. morning}
<A>__{shifty steps out the front door to look about. it's a nice day. he looks up and down the street, nothing. he goes to walk back in the house when suddenly his eye catches something on the floor. he reaches down and picks up a large jiffy envelope that's been left leaning against the bin cupboard. scribed across the front is: shifty}
<L>__{interior rez's house shifty's bedroom. morning}
